418
00:31:25,901 --> 00:31:26,985
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana dengan
Presedir Mo Seung Jae?</font>

419
00:31:27,069 --> 00:31:29,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia berinvestasi
di filmnya Woon Gwang.</font>

420
00:31:30,989 --> 00:31:32,408
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami baik-baik saja.</font>

421
00:31:32,491 --> 00:31:35,035
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi dia orang yang berbahaya.</font>

422
00:31:35,828 --> 00:31:37,955
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harus selalu berhati-hati.
