<font color=#FFFF00>Hei. Tulis dulu sebelum aku lupa.</font>

432
00:32:11,488 --> 00:32:14,616
<font color=#FFFF00>Tiga, enam, delapan, sembilan.</font>

433
00:32:14,700 --> 00:32:17,411
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tak habis pikir
